       Map&lt;String, String&gt; map = new HashMap&lt;&gt;();
       map.put(&quot;cce0&quot;,&quot;frityyy&quot;);
       return ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.OK).body(map);
   }
   ```
OR  

Solution 2.

Modify your existing code to either of the following ways.

