`s` is never added to anything, so it will never be painted.

`this.setPreferredSize(new Dimension((frame.getWidth()/3),frame.getHeight()));` is a horribly bad idea.  The window should be conforming to the size of the components, not the other way round.  In fact, there&#39;s never really a good reason to expose `MyFrame` to the components this way, it provides these components control over `MyFrame` which they should never have.

